Class CassandraAdminDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tmobile.opensource.casquatch.CassandraDriver
      • com.tmobile.opensource.casquatch.CassandraAdminDriver

  • public class CassandraAdminDriver
extends CassandraDriver
    This object provides an advanced interface for connecting to Cassandra clusters within SDE which allows for functionality that through the abstraction and thus requires DSE imports.

        Parameters:
        username - Name of User

        contactPoints - Comma separated list of contact points for Cassandra cluster. Order is ignored.
        port - Port Cassandra is listening on. Typically 9042

        keyspace - Default keyspace
